channel.title: Urgent!
channel.description:
Hello I could really use some help I started using a different client with my PI source and I get this -It freezes 5 minutes in -I get over a 100 errors -I have no idea whats wrong -Please help me?
[img]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h381/raylaw1/Screenshot_2_zpsad83ca04.png[/img]
[img]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h381/raylaw1/Screenshot_3_zpsf0a0c5d8.png[/img]
[img]http://i1107.photobucket.com/albums/h381/raylaw1/image_zps15bc0b9b.png[/img]
Seriously I am stumped it was all working perfect now its just not!

item.title: Urgent!
item.dc:creator: @RUNE-PK RUNE-PK
item.description:
@RUNE-PK wrote:

[quote=“CoderOops, post:2, topic:539705”]It does not load cache correctly, and that’s why it freezes your client.

Take everything away what you did add, and redo it in pieces or so, to see where’s the problem.[/quote]

Okay thanks I fixed it
